title: LUXURIOUS BRICKELL FLATIRON!!
posting_body: ['Brickell Flatiron offers 1 bed/1 bath with 730 SF.', 'Enjoy a large balcony with Italian porcelain tile flooring, floor to ceiling windows and an enhanced insulation sound proofing between units.', 'Beautiful city views!.', "Brickell Flatiron's amenities include the 64th floor rooftop pool with a spa, and 6,300-square-foot gym with a Pilates, yoga, aerobics studio, and a juice bar.", 'The building also includes a lap pool and children’s pool on the 18th floor, a movie theater, billiards and cigar room, wine cellar, and electric car charging stations.', 'In the heart of Brickell this gorgeous building is the ultimate address in town.', 'Easy to show!', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
